data.description: You must see this adorable 3 bedroom home with 3 full bathrooms and NO HOA.  Primary and a second bedroom has full ensuite. You have never seen 1344 sq ft look so very spacious.  Beautiful granite throughout the kitchen and bathrooms. Nice front porch for your rockers and great covered back patio for grilling and a FANTASTIC deck in the back for your fire pit and additional sitting area.  Very close to shopping and the Greenville square. Refrigerator stays with the property.  Taxes are very reasonable, no HOA and quick access to I30.  Don't miss it.
